			</div>
			<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tight bg-gradient-to-r from-zinc-100 via-zinc-400 to-zinc-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
				Custom WordPress <br/> Architecture.
			</h1>
			<p class="text-zinc-400 max-w-xl text-lg font-light leading-relaxed">
				Hi, I'm Ali Hassan. I engineer high-performance headless WordPress themes and custom frontend ecosystems that load instantly and scale globally.
			</p>
		</div>
	</ScrollSection>

	<ScrollSection id="architecture" className="bg-transparent border-b border-zinc-900 z-10">
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
			<div class="p-8 border border-zinc-900 bg-zinc-950/80 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl space-y-4 hover:border-teal-500/50 transition-colors">
				<LayoutTemplate class="w-8 h-8 text-sky-400" />
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Custom Theme Dev</h3>
				<p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Building bespoke WordPress themes from scratch without bloated page builders, ensuring pixel-perfect design translation.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="p-8 border border-zinc-900 bg-zinc-950/80 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl space-y-4 hover:border-teal-500/50 transition-colors">
				<Zap class="w-8 h-8 text-teal-400" />
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Headless Ecosystems</h3>
				<p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Decoupling the WordPress CMS via REST API or GraphQL to feed lightning-fast frontend frameworks like React and Svelte.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="p-8 border border-zinc-900 bg-zinc-950/80 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl space-y-4 hover:border-teal-500/50 transition-colors">
				<Database class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-400" />
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Advanced Data Structuring</h3>
				<p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Expert implementation of Custom Post Types (CPTs) and Advanced Custom Fields (ACF) for complex enterprise content.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</ScrollSection>

	<ScrollSection id="projects" className="bg-transparent z-10 py-24">
		<div class="w-full space-y-20">
			<div class="border-b border-zinc-900 pb-6 flex justify-between items-end mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">Featured Deployments</h2>
			</div>
			
			<div class="project-card group border border-zinc-900 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-zinc-950/80 backdrop-blur-md hover:bg-zinc-900/50 transition-all flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
