				</div>
				<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4">
					<span class="text-xs font-mono text-sky-400">HEALTHCARE INFRASTRUCTURE</span>
					<h4 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-100">Candi Health</h4>
					<p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">A secure, highly professional corporate architecture designed for the healthcare sector. Engineered for high accessibility scores, rapid load times, and seamless user routing.</p>
					<a href="https://candihealth.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-medium hover:text-sky-400 transition-colors mt-4">
						View Live Site <ArrowUpRight class="w-4 h-4" />
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="project-card group border border-zinc-900 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-zinc-950/80 backdrop-blur-md hover:bg-zinc-900/50 transition-all flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center mt-4">
				<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 bg-zinc-900 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 overflow-hidden relative group-hover:border-purple-400/50 transition-colors shadow-2xl">
					<img src="/images/estate.jpg" alt="Estate Law Atlanta" class="w-full h-auto object-cover opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-700 ease-out" />
				</div>
				<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4">
					<span class="text-xs font-mono text-purple-400">LEAD GENERATION & LEGAL</span>
					<h4 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-100">Estate Law Atlanta</h4>
					<p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">A high-conversion custom theme built to drive trust and client acquisition. Integrates dynamic contact structures and localized SEO optimization directly into the theme layer.</p>
					<a href="https://estatelawatlanta.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-medium hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors mt-4">
						View Live Site <ArrowUpRight class="w-4 h-4" />
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="project-card group border border-zinc-900 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-zinc-950/80 backdrop-blur-md hover:bg-zinc-900/50 transition-all flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-8 items-center mt-4">
				<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 bg-zinc-900 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 overflow-hidden relative group-hover:border-rose-400/50 transition-colors shadow-2xl">
					<img src="/images/breaking.jpg" alt="Breaking the Cycle" class="w-full h-auto object-cover opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-700 ease-out" />
				</div>
				<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4">
					<span class="text-xs font-mono text-rose-400">NON-PROFIT PORTAL</span>
					<h4 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-100">Breaking the Cycle</h4>
					<p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Accessible, impact-driven web architecture for foster care advocacy. Built with intuitive content management capabilities to empower organizational teams without technical overhead.</p>
					<a href="https://breakingthecycle-fostercare.org/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-medium hover:text-rose-400 transition-colors mt-4">
						View Live Site <ArrowUpRight class="w-4 h-4" />
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="project-card group border border-zinc-900 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-zinc-950/80 backdrop-blur-md hover:bg-zinc-900/50 transition-all flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center mt-4">
				<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 bg-zinc-900 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 overflow-hidden relative group-hover:border-yellow-400/50 transition-colors shadow-2xl">
					<img src="/images/ssadvertise.jpg" alt="SS Advertise" class="w-full h-auto object-cover opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-700 ease-out" />
				</div>
				<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4">
					<span class="text-xs font-mono text-yellow-400">MARKETING AGENCY</span>
					<h4 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-100">SS Advertise</h4>
					<p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">A bold, highly interactive corporate profile designed to showcase marketing services. Engineered for rapid Largest Contentful Paint (LCP) times to maximize ad conversion retention.</p>
					<a href="https://www.ssadvertise.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-medium hover:text-yellow-400 transition-colors mt-4">
						View Live Site <ArrowUpRight class="w-4 h-4" />
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="project-card group border border-zinc-900 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-zinc-950/80 backdrop-blur-md hover:bg-zinc-900/50 transition-all flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-8 items-center mt-4">
				<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 bg-zinc-900 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 overflow-hidden relative group-hover:border-indigo-400/50 transition-colors shadow-2xl">
					<img src="/images/elevated.jpg" alt="Elevated Video Solutions" class="w-full h-auto object-cover opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-700 ease-out" />
				</div>
				<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4">
					<span class="text-xs font-mono text-indigo-400">MEDIA PRODUCTION</span>
					<h4 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-100">Elevated Video Solutions</h4>
					<p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">A media-heavy custom WordPress environment optimized for high-definition video backgrounds and portfolio galleries, utilizing aggressive lazy-loading techniques.</p>
