					<h4 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-100">Donatefy</h4>
					<p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Secure data structuring for non-profit donation streams. Features bespoke Custom Post Types (CPTs) and seamless payment gateway integrations managed within the WP dashboard.</p>
					<a href="https://www.donatefy.org/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-medium hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors mt-4">
						View Live Site <ArrowUpRight class="w-4 h-4" />
