				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="project-card group border border-zinc-900 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-zinc-950/80 backdrop-blur-md hover:bg-zinc-900/50 transition-all flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-8 items-center mt-4">
				<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 bg-zinc-900 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 overflow-hidden relative group-hover:border-blue-400/50 transition-colors shadow-2xl">
					<img src="/images/americloud.jpg" alt="AmeriCloud Telecom" class="w-full h-auto object-cover opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-700 ease-out" />
				</div>
				<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4">
					<span class="text-xs font-mono text-blue-400">B2B CORPORATE</span>
					<h4 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-100">AmeriCloud Telecom</h4>
					<p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Enterprise-grade architecture for telecommunications. Built to scale with complex B2B service offerings, utilizing rigorous structural hierarchies for maximum SEO indexability.</p>
					<a href="https://telecom.americloudmarketing.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-medium hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors mt-4">
